title: Tech Live 2023: What’s Next for OpenAI? | WSJ Tech News Briefing
description:
The company at the center of the generative artificial intelligence revolution took the stage at the WSJ’s Tech Live event. 

OpenAI’s CEO Sam Altman and CTO Mira Murati sat down with WSJ senior personal tech columnist Joanna Stern to talk about AGI, the capabilities of future GPT models and more. Julie Chang hosts.

Tech News Briefing
WSJ’s tech podcast featuring breaking news, scoops and tips on tech innovations and policy debates, plus exclusive interviews with movers and shakers in the industry.
